edente,donación alimentos restaurantes,reducir desperdicio comida,plataforma donación alimentos gratis,food donation,surplus food,economía circular,food waste reduction\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"ComidaConecta — Donación de excedente alimentario\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Plataforma gratuita que conecta comercios con excedente alimentario y entidades sociales. Sin comisiones.\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"es_ES\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"http://localhost:3000/logo.svg\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"512\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"512\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"ComidaConecta\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"ComidaConecta — Donación de excedente alimentario\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Plataforma gratuita que conecta comercios con excedente alimentario y entidades sociales. Sin comisiones.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"http://localhost:3000/logo.svg\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:alt\" content=\"ComidaConecta\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:width\" content=\"512\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:height\" content=\"512\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/logo.svg\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/logo.svg\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-svh flex flex-col bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-100 antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div style=\"visibility:hidden\"><nav class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 bg-zinc-950/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-zinc-800\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-leaf w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">ComidaConecta</span></a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg>Volver al inicio</a></div></nav><section class=\"pt-32 pb-16 px-4 text-center bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-950 via-zinc-900 to-zinc-950\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-emerald-900/40 border border-emerald-700/30 rounded-full text-emerald-300 text-xs font-medium mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-3.5 h-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg>Contribución voluntaria</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6\">Ayuda a mantener<!-- --> <span class=\"text-emerald-400\">ComidaConecta</span> activa</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8\">ComidaConecta es <strong>gratuita para entidades sociales</strong> y de uso gratuito para comercios. Las contribuciones voluntarias ayudan a mantener la plataforma y a conectar más donaciones. Si en el futuro se estableciera algún modelo de suscripción, se comunicaría previamente sin afectar a las donaciones ya realizadas.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/30 rounded-full text-xs text-zinc-400\">💚 Sin contrato ni permanencia</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/30 rounded-full text-xs text-zinc-400\">🎯 100% a la plataforma</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/30 rounded-full text-xs text-zinc-400\">🤝 Ayuda a conectar más donaciones</span></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-24 px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-zinc-800/30 border border-zinc-700/30 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-emerald-700/30 transition-colors flex flex-col\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/40 border border-emerald-700/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-smartphone w-7 h-7 text-emerald-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"20\" x=\"5\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">Bizum</h2><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-6 flex-1\">Desde tu app bancaria. Rápido, sin comisiones.</p><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-4 font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white shadow-emerald-900/30 hover:shadow-emerald-700/30\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-smartphone w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"20\" x=\"5\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path></svg>Donar con Bizum</button><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-4 text-center leading-relaxed\">Abre tu app bancaria → «Enviar dinero» → «A un número» → pega el número (se copia al hacer clic)</p></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-800/30 border border-zinc-700/30 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-emerald-700/30 transition-colors flex flex-col\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-blue-900/40 border border-blue-700/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-credit-card w-7 h-7 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"5\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"2\" x2=\"22\" y1=\"10\" y2=\"10\"></line></svg></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">PayPal</h2><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-6 flex-1\">Tarjeta o cuenta PayPal. Seguro y rápido.</p><a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/A3AFSXGDR3UE6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-4 font-semibold rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/30 hover:shadow-blue-700/30 transition-all duration-200\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-credit-card w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"5\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"2\" x2=\"22\" y1=\"10\" y2=\"10\"></line></svg>Donar con PayPal</a><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-4 text-center leading-relaxed\">Se abre PayPal en una ventana segura. No guardamos tus datos de pago.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-3 px-6 py-4 bg-zinc-800/20 border border-zinc-700/20 rounded-xl hover:bg-zinc-800/40 transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wallet w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 7V4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h15a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4h-3a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h3a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-2a1 1 0 0 0-1-1\"></path><path d=\"M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h15a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-zinc-400 font-medium\">Donar con cripto (BEP20)</span></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"mt-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-zinc-800/20 border border-zinc-700/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400 mx-auto mb-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">No olvides que lo esencial es gratis</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">ComidaConecta es <strong>gratuita para entidades sociales</strong>. Para comercios el uso es gratuito y las contribuciones son voluntarias. Si en el futuro se estableciera algún modelo de suscripción, se comunicaría previamente sin afectar a las donaciones ya realizadas.<!-- --> <strong class=\"text-zinc-400\"> Lo importante es que sigas conectando excedente con necesidad</strong>.</p></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-zinc-800 py-12 px-4 bg-zinc-950\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-leaf w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-semibold\">ComidaConecta</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-zinc-500\"><a class=\"hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/aviso-legal\">Aviso Legal</a><a class=\"hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/privacidad\">Privacidad</a><a class=\"hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/cookies\">Cookies</a><a class=\"hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/condiciones\">Condiciones</a></div><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-600\">© 2026 ComidaConecta. Reduciendo el desperdicio, una donación a la vez.</p></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"fixed bottom-4 right-4 z-50 flex flex-col gap-2\"></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/10qk6v6416kh8.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[72849,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0s1qbjflqyc99.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.j